{"tid":920549,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣站沉降醜聞　紅區選民照投陳","createTime":"2018-11-29T01:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T04:34:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"beee31b6db158054b76251b416ba2715b73125b8","tid":920549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:36:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181129/20557199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F20557199&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=2954aab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F20557199&h=5fe4e1bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181129/20557199</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月29日 <br />\n<br />\n土瓜灣站沉降醜聞　紅區選民照投陳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181129/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181129%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=3513b926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵沙中綫土瓜灣站的沉降醜聞滿城風雨，民主派一直力倡以特權法徹查，惟追求公義真相似乎未能令向來支持建制的紅區選民「轉軚」。《蘋果》統計8個土瓜灣區內點票結果，發現兩大陣營在3.11及11.25兩次補選得票相若。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得票高於李馮總和<br />\n<br />\n年初3.11補選，民主派於土瓜灣共7個票站奪得11,763票，佔總票數47.1%，建制派民建聯鄭泳舜則奪得13,209票，佔52.9%；及至11.25補選，土瓜灣有8個票站，提倡於立法會引用特權法徹查沙中綫醜聞的民主派李卓人取得10,416票，佔總票數42%，馮檢基則有1,073票，佔4.3%，二人合共得票46.3%，較姚松炎得票微跌；相對未有表明要以特權法徹查真相，僅關注居民賠償問題的陳凱欣，李、馮二人得票不及她一人的12,993票多，得票率為52.4%。<br />\n<br />\n曾在立法會提出引用特權法徹查沙中綫醜聞的民主黨林卓廷指，不能單從今次選舉結果有五成人投票支持陳凱欣就斷言市民不支持徹查，指選民投票尚受其他因素，包括候選人、政治立場等，「除非有選後票站調查先知，否則變成憑空猜測」。他又指，土瓜灣居民受沙中綫沉降影響程度有異，各人關注程度不同，但無論建制派如何演繹，「啱就啱，唔啱就唔啱，都係咁跟進」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n建制地膽箍票　未「欣」外人揸流攤<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n警司：催淚彈傷害性低於警棍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建制地膽箍票　未「欣」外人揸流攤<br />\n到立會大樓履新即犯禁違規帶家人合照　陳凱欣反怪保安"},{"pid":"5b79847dde538fc7f4d07785764d57dc96c19cd0","tid":920549,"uid":44823,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7804150870fdefb7b0e6687e9f775253b480114b","tid":920549,"uid":47359,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:42:32.000Z","msg":"因為真正支持民主嘅人個人會醒啲<br />\n唔會含撚投泛民<br />\n<br />\n2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=7b8891b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=2eecde69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=42057698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=1aa6de8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=8%2F8z883Pf3IVZkbh3r2cI9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=896271ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"229c0037cb183b83026c8a77ebdff1e831bf504f","tid":920549,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱答得我未?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/THL8ca3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTHL8ca3.png&h=2c4094a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"964b044a12a9e12c673feb35ab952bc8a3b6bffc","tid":920549,"uid":10064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"沉左落地底都抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca118252d2c0a4fccb5e42cac3af16c11b8333c0","tid":920549,"uid":9217,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:49:55.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢老地區注定一定係多建制<br />\n而且而家都大把人唔出黎投泛民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba1968acf8f424f3ae746dba5150e20ab9841ff","tid":920549,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"樓主你唔好再賴選民<br />\n投親中派嘅人未必多咗<br />\n只係少咗人投泛民"},{"pid":"ba7d7d401f2227b7d17d77ec8d0d4dd4928bd6ef","tid":920549,"uid":51920,"like":0